Column Description: In ArcGIS, a system-managed value that uniquely identifies a record or feature.
Census 2010 ZIP Code Tabulation Area code
State FIPS Code + County FIPS Code (if non-metro) or HUD Fair Market Rent (FMR) Metropolitan Area (HFMA) code (if small-area)
County Name (if non-metro) or HFMA Name (if small area)
Type of DDA; NM for non-metro, SA for small area
